{"tid":1712084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［中大］大家同我立即幫中大手","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T13:48:11.000Z","uid":204398,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1db9f74fbfa1b2fc1152e31c54d4ff154158a09","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係叫你哋上山</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaBYne4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaBYne4.jpg&h=93802891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部狗都入緊中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲上去咩<br />\n但係你唔通要中大人頂曬全部狗？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家立刻同我遍地開佢老母花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分散警力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d809e54c8185bdf1b1f651d79e14b612c58a22b7","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係要依家一兩區開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係每區都要</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6166681db91fc7da90a8c5d2b885e91a07627340","tid":1712084,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"遠水不能救近火！！只係各地開花，班狗可以用無警時份唔理你！！<br />\n<br />\n分頭行事！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主力反包！<br />\n另小隊開花！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中大地理難去，但去到就去！人多就咩都有可能！求下大家！！"},{"pid":"2eefa6516b8dfc5f556f1ecb4fa09660f008d527","tid":1712084,"uid":195084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"錯撚哂<br />\n集中沙田附近既區啦屌<br />\n你十八區開花<br />\n人又少<br />\n佢又唔撚理你<br />\n照入車去屠城"},{"pid":"f75e790a98c3fe08055735c0726fed9dec021595","tid":1712084,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"屌吖, 個副校仲話同指揮官夾左, green object會撤退"},{"pid":"65ce3d4bfb2ee98846168b6594bdfa7c69cff138","tid":1712084,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:30:48.000Z","msg":"！！！中大告急，中大告急！！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出唔到去嘅人</span></span>幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7dB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=1edee549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n今日Task分類<br />\n/task1: 中環罷工<br />\n/task2: 其他中國同香港議題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">/task3: </span></span>:warning:中大 :warning:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前線手足咁撚辛苦，你哋班冷氣軍師唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">做晒嘢就好去其他戰線啦，Reddit嗰啲都唔夠人呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n(突發）幫手救中大（twitter戰線）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n出唔到去幫手嘅連登仔同我入嚟，唔好偷懶<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1711964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1711964</a>"},{"pid":"112284ba1222b0e6c491bcd5acd8cc2f7df41e49","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eefa6516b8dfc5f556f1ecb4fa09660f008d527","tid":1712084,"uid":195084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"錯撚哂<br />\n集中沙田附近既區啦屌<br />\n你十八區開花<br />\n人又少<br />\n佢又唔撚理你<br />\n照入車去屠城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"講真你依家其他區嘅人都唔會去到中大附近<br />\n每區都開先俾到壓力佢哋，佢哋要調配人力一定會亂<br />\n有啲區啲狗去唔到就當快閃，夠人又快閃班狗又想理咪一定要調啲警力過去，咁當然有啲區見到唔夠人就自然唔好開波"},{"pid":"c21fdf940668ad625d41f5c954ef5ceb7dd35635","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259533b02fdc91c04bc4b79194ca1965ea88b7c3","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"幫幫中大人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499ff48c80318d13b0eb7c290a73c114bb4330a6","tid":1712084,"uid":97104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人係食屎狗咋, 個個都無撚用嫁</span>"},{"pid":"60771d10e2fdb9ffb6e9735773dafb3060bad1e7","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"暴大情況危急呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0535e40cafe6e2d9aabc1050c5b85f4bb29dfdc1","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be92acd3834d496168c4efaa0939b08083a62981","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5f4957f78df8b69fc03c50b1aab8affad104875","tid":1712084,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEAeFaD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2